title: fanoutqa: Find the richest 5 people in the world. Which university/high school did they graduate from? (8d2bb1a2fbcab9d4)

chat_history.content: Find the richest 5 people in the world. Which university/high school did they graduate from?

According to Bloomberg, the five richest people in the world are:
1. Elon Musk (net worth $194 billion) - University of Pennsylvania (BS in economics and BS in physics) and Wharton School of the University of Pennsylvania (undergraduate degree in business)
2. Bernard Arnault (net worth $166 billion) - École Polytechnique (diploma)
3. Jeff Bezos (net worth $111 billion) - Princeton University (BS in computer science and electrical engineering)
4. Bill Gates (net worth $102 billion) - Harvard University (dropout)
5. Warren Buffett (net worth $100 billion) - University of Nebraska–Lincoln (BS in business administration) and Columbia University (MS in economics)

functions.desc:
Ask a capable helper for help looking up a piece of information or performing an action.
Do not simply repeat what the user said as instructions.
You should use this to break up complex user queries into multiple simpler steps.
NOTE: Helpers cannot see previous parts of your conversation.
